A joyful winter scene in Studio Ghibli style: A wooden sled races down a pristine snow-covered mountain slope, leaving a trail of powder in its wake. Pine trees heavy with fresh snow line the path, their branches drooping gracefully. In the background, a cozy rustic mountain hut with warm amber light glowing from its windows sits perched on the hillside, smoke curling from its chimney into the soft lavender-pink winter sky. The composition captures the exhilaration of the downhill rush contrasted with the welcoming warmth waiting above. Soft, painterly brushstrokes, warm and cool color harmony typical of Miyazaki films, with delicate snowflakes drifting through the air and a sense of nostalgic winter magic.
